      <title>研究发现，反 LGBTQ 法律使乌干达损失 16 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-10/anti-lgbtq-laws-cost-uganda-1-6-billion-study-finds-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项新研究发现，乌干达的反 LGBTQ 法律（包括在某些情况下判处死刑）自去年 5 月推出以来，已给该国造成高达 16 亿美元的损失。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-10/anti-lgbtq-laws-cost-uganda-1-6-billion-study-finds-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 06:44:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>香港 ETF 投资者创纪录押注股市下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/hong-kong-etf-investors-make-record-bet-on-stock-market-decline</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港的投资者已将创纪录的金额押注于在股市下跌时获利的交易所交易基金，这表明在股市大幅上涨之后，市场情绪的变化非常快。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/hong-kong-etf-investors-make-record-bet-on-stock-market-decline</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 06:40:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度将建造核潜艇、购买无人机以对抗中国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/india-to-build-nuclear-submarines-buy-drones-to-counter-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，印度将建造两艘核动力潜艇，并购买 31 架美国制造的远程无人机，预计耗资 3500 亿卢比（42 亿美元），以帮助对抗中国在该地区的军事主导地位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/india-to-build-nuclear-submarines-buy-drones-to-counter-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 06:38:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>1490亿美元资金外流后中国加强对理财产品的审查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/china-steps-up-checks-of-wealth-management-products-after-149-billion-outflow</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，在投资者为追逐股市上涨而撤出约 1,490 亿美元资金后，中国已要求金融机构加强对国内理财产品的监控。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/china-steps-up-checks-of-wealth-management-products-after-149-billion-outflow</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 06:30:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>优衣库母公司瞄准强劲的西方市场，力争提高销售额</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/uniqlo-owner-s-earnings-beat-eyes-bigger-sales-in-fiscal-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[迅销株式会社 (Fast Retailing Co.) 在向西方新市场扩张的过程中帮助这家日本服装店运营商抵消了中国市场经济放缓的影响，因此该公司计划在 2025 财年实现更高的销售额。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/uniqlo-owner-s-earnings-beat-eyes-bigger-sales-in-fiscal-2025</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 06:13:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>投资者为 CPI 做准备，卖出日元成为“最受欢迎的交易”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/sell-yen-is-most-popular-trade-as-investors-brace-for-cpi-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着投资者为可能扰乱金融市场的美国月度通胀数据做准备，“抛售日本货币”正成为越来越流行的口号。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/sell-yen-is-most-popular-trade-as-investors-brace-for-cpi-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
